   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="Edgeworth_Princeton_1838_04_page01.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <dateline>
                  <placeName ref="Id_where"/>
                  <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#New-Burlington-Street_ENK">New Burlington Street</placeName>
                  <date when="1838-04-06">April 6 1838</date>
               </dateline>
               <salute>
                  <persName>Madam</persName>
               </salute>
            </opener>
            <p>
               I do myself the pleasure of<lb/>
               transmitting to you an early copy of<lb/>
               the <title ref="./Workography.xml#Memoi6">Memoirs of Sir William <choice>
                     <orig>Knighten</orig>
                     <reg>Knighton</reg>
                  </choice>
               </title>
               <lb/>
               which will be published in a few days,<lb/>
               thinking that it may <del>tr</del> be likely to<lb/>
               afford you some entertainment<lb/>
            </p>
            <p>
               It has given me much <choice>
                  <orig>satis-<lb/>
                  faction</orig>
                  <reg>satisfaction</reg>
               </choice> to hear from <persName ref="./Personography.xml#WilsL1">Mr Lestock<lb/>
               Wilson</persName> that I am to have the <choice>
                  <orig>ho-<lb/>
               nor</orig>
                  <reg>honor</reg>
               </choice> of including <title ref="./Workography.xml#Helen1">"Helen"</title> in my<lb/>
            </p>
            <p>
               <pb n="2" facs="Edgeworth_Princeton_1838_04_page02.jpg"/>
               series of "Standard Novels"<lb/>
            </p>
            <closer>
               I have the honor to be<lb/>
               Madam<lb/>
               Your faithful Servant<lb/>
               <persName ref="./Personography.xml#BentR1">Richard Bentley</persName>
               <lb/>
            </closer>
            <closer>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>To <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeM1">Miss Edgeworth</persName>
                  </addrLine>
                  <lb/>
               </address>
            </closer>
         </div>
